OL,3,CPolling stations open in England,
OL,4,CScotland and Wales
OL,6,FPolling stations across Wales,
OL,7,FScotland and parts of England have
OL,8,Fopened for millions to cast their vote
OL,9,Fin the biggest round of elections
OL,10,Fsince the general election in 2024.
OL,12,FAlmost 25,000 candidates are fighting
OL,13,Fto be elected to more than 5,000 seats
OL,14,Fon 136 councils across England.
OL,16,FIn Scotland, all 129 seats are up for
OL,17,Felection at Holyrood while voters in
OL,18,FWales will choose 96 members of the
OL,19,FSenedd.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/2
