OL,3,CPolling stations open in England,
OL,4,CScotland and Wales
OL,6,FThe polls close at 10pm, but unlike in
OL,7,Fgeneral elections, results won't be
OL,8,Fcounted as quickly, with only a third
OL,9,Fof authorities doing so overnight.
OL,11,FThe first results are expected around
OL,12,F1am on Friday.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
